Package appt

package appt
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AdminUI
    Provides the user interface for an administrator to view and manage appointment schedules.
    Appointment
    Abstract class representing an appointment.
    ApptController
    Controller class for managing appointments.
    ApptData
    Manages appointment data, including reading from, writing to, and updating appointments in a CSV file.
    DoctorAppointment
    Represents a doctor's appointment, extending the base Appointment class.
    DoctorUI
    The DoctorUI class provides a user interface for doctors, allowing them to view, edit, and manage their schedules and appointments.
    PatientUI
    The PatientUI class provides a user interface for patients to view, manage, and book appointments.
